        ('Power bank', 'power-bank', 12, '&lt;h2&gt;Power Bank&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Texnika asrida bizga yordamchi bo&rsquo;lgan smartfon, planshet, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/noutbuki-planshety-kompyutery/noutbuki&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;noutbu&lt;/strong&gt;k&lt;/a&gt; singari ko&rsquo;plab elektron qurilmalar hayotimizning ajralmas qismiga aylandi. Odamlar kerakli ma&#039;lumotlarni tez va oson topishga, shuningdek, doimo aloqada bo&#039;lishga intiladilar. Ammo, har bir jihozning kamchiligi uning quvvat energiyasini ekanligini hisobga olsak power banklar buning ajoyib yechimidir. Power Bank so&rsquo;zi tarjima qilinganda- tashqi quvvatlantirish qurilmasi degan ma&rsquo;noni beradi. Bu qurilma ayniqsa, sayohatchilar va gadjetlarni sevuvchilar uchun juda qo&rsquo;l keladi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Tashqi quvvatlantirish qurilmasining (Power Bank) asosiy xususiyatlari quyidagilardan iborat:&lt;br /&gt;&bull; dizayn va o&#039;lchami;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; batareya quvvati;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; ulagich turi&lt;br /&gt;&bull; qo&#039;shimcha funktsiyalar;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; narx va ishlab chiqaruvchi.&lt;br /&gt;Nimaga e&#039;tibor berish kerak va qaysi quvvat bankini tanlash kerak?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Quvvat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Har qanday quvvat manbai uchun sig&#039;im asosiy ko&#039;rsatkichdir. Avvalo, siz qaysi qurilma uchun quvvat bankini tanlashingizni hal qilishingiz kerak. Masalan:&lt;br /&gt;&bull; 5000 mA / soatgacha bo&#039;lgan Powerbank quvvati kichik batareyali smartfonlar uchun, shuningdek, eng tejamkor foydalanuvchilar uchun javob beradi. Bundan tashqari, bunday modellar ixcham bo&rsquo;lib 