ets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Eng sifatli va arzon Power Bank sotib olish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Olcha.uz onlayn-do&#039;koni &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/telefony-gadzhety-aksessuary/telefony&quot;&gt;smartfonlar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; va gadjetlar uchun aksesuarlarining keng assortimentini taklif etadi. Uyingizdan chiqmagan holda O&rsquo;zbekistonning istalgan yeridan telefoningiz uchun tashqi batareya sotib olishingiz mumkin, mutaxassislarimizning malakali maslahati sizga to&#039;g&#039;ri xarid qilishingizda yordam beradi. Awei, PNY, Promate, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/manufacturer/hoco&quot;&gt;Hoco&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, Joyroom, XO, Ttec, Remax, Xiaomi kabi yirik va ishonchli kompaniyalarning keng turdagi modellarini muddatli to&rsquo;lov asosida ham xarid qilish imkoniyatiga egasiz. Buning uchun passport hamda bank kartasi kifoya.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&rsquo;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumotlarni sayt orqali javob olishingiz yoki +998(71)2022021 raqamidan foydalanishingiz mumkin. O&rsquo;zbekiston bo&rsquo;ylab yetkazib berish xizmati mavjud.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
