        ('Tennis anjomlari', 'vse-dlya-tennisa', 81, '&lt;div&gt;&lt;h1 class=&quot;text-4xl font-bold text-c-gray-6 mb-4&quot;&gt;Sport anjomlari&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Agar siz tennisni yaxshi ko&#039;rsangiz, o&#039;zingizni mukammal jismoniy shaklda saqlamoqchi bo&#039;lsangiz, doimo yaxshi kayfiyatda bo&#039;ling va o&#039;zingizni mukammal jihozlanganligingizga amin bo&#039;ling. Shundan so&#039;ng, siz to&#039;g&#039;ri tanlovni amalga oshirasiz. Siz aynan bizda eng yaxshi ishlab chiqaruvchilarning qulay tennis o&#039;yinlarini topishingiz mumkin. Biz nafaqat Toshkent balki butun O&#039;zbekiston bo&#039;ylab etkazib beramiz. Olcha.uz dan sifatli va kafolatga ega maxsulotlarni sotib oling.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Qanday qilib sotib olishim mumkin?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bizning onlayn-do&#039;konimizda siz bizning veb-saytimiz orqali uydan chiqmasdan buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Katalogda turli modellar va ularning narxi, tashqi ko&#039;rinishi va ranglari mavjud. Bundan tashqari, biz boshqa sport uskunalarini ham taqdim etamiz. Agar sizning byudjetingizda bir vaqtning o&#039;zida bunday mablag &#039; bo&#039;lmasa, ortiqcha to&#039;lovsiz to&#039;lash imkoniyati mavjud. O&#039;zbekiston bo&#039;ylab yetkazib berish mumkin. Belgilangan joyga qarab 4 soatdan 2 ish kuniga etkazib berish.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&#039;lumotni +998 71-2022021 yoki bizning saytimiz orqali chat orqali olishingiz mumkin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
        ('Jang san’ati uchun anjomlar', 'vse-dlya-edinoborstv', 81, 'Jiddiy sport turlari nafaqat kundalik mashg&#039;ulotlarni, balki sertifikatlangan uskunalarni ham talab qiladi. Kurashning qaysi turini tanlamang, u kikboksing, tay boksi, taekvondo, djujitsu, qo&#039;l jangi yoki muaytay bo&#039;lsin, olimlar va sport shifokorlari tomonidan ishlab chiqilgan maxsus kiyim va himoya vositalarisiz mashq qilish shunchaki xavfli. Biz nafaqat Toshkent balki butun O&#039;zbekiston bo&#039;ylab etkazib beramiz. Olcha.uz dan sifatli va kafolaga ega maxsulotlarni harid qiling.', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
        ('Smart Watches', 'smart-watches', 9, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Smart Watches&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Smart watches (Aqlli soat) - bu bilakga taqish uchun mo&#039;ljallangan mobil qurilma. U qo&#039;l soatiga juda o&#039;xshasa-da, ixchamroq hajmda smartfonga xos funksiyalarga ega. Ular hisob-&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/ru/category/knigi&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;kitoblar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, vaqtni aytib berish, tarjima qilish, fitnesni kuzatish va hatto o&#039;yin o&#039;ynash kabi keng ko&#039;lamli vazifalarni bajaradi. Aqlli soatlar hozirda tobora ommalashib bormoqda. Bir qator foydali funksiyalarni taqdim eta oladigan ushbu mobil qurilmalarni sotib olishda Olcha.uz sizga yordam beradi!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;O&rsquo;zbekstondagi eng yaxshi smart watch (aqlli soatlar) qaysi?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Tanlash uchun son-sanoqsiz smart watch (aqlli soat) &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/ru/manufacturer/apple&quot;&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, Samsung, Xiaomi,Asus,Haylou,Pandora,Montblanc,Honor,Redmi,Amazit,Blacview,Kuplace,Hoco,Porodo, Artel kabi brend modellari va gadjetlat uchun aksessuarlari ham mavjud, lekin ularni quyidagi funksiyalariga ko&rsquo;ra toifalarga ajratish mumkin: &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&bull; Fitness aqlli soatlari:&lt;/strong&gt; Ular fitnesni hisobga olgan holda ishlab chiqilgan bo&lsquo;lib, fitnes va hayot tarzidagi o&rsquo;zgarishlarni kuzatish uchun bir qator funksiyalarni taklif etadi. Nafaqat sportchilar balki siz uchun ham bunday soatlar ajoyib tanlov bo&#039;l