        ('Avtomobil uchun audio', 'audio-1', 170, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Avtomobil uchun audio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Avtomobil audiosi - bu avtomobilda tovush hosil qilib uni kuchaytirib berishni ta&#039;minlaydigan qurilmalar to&rsquo;plami. Bizning do&#039;konda siz avtomobilga mos bo&#039;lgan hamma narsani sotib olishingiz mumkin. Avtomobil akustikasi mashina haydash paytida musiqa tinglashni yaxshi ko&#039;radigan haydovchilar uchun juda zarur.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ovoz sifati va quvvatini yaxshilash uchun quyidagilar qo&#039;llaniladi: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &bull; sabvuferlar- ovozli signal yuqori, o&#039;rta va past chastotalarga bo&#039;linishi mumkin. &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/avtomobilnye-aksessuary/audio-1/sabvufery&quot;&gt;Sabvufer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; past chastotalarni qayta ishlab chiqaradi. Kompozitsiyaning ovozi chiroyli, bass esa jonli musiqa kabi aniq bo&#039;lishi uchun sotib olishga arziydi; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; kuchaytirgichlar- ovozni pasaytirib tinglashda ham ovoz sifatini yaxshilashga qaratilgan. Karnaylar orqali musiqa tinglashda paydo bo&#039;ladigan shovqinlarni bartaraf etadi. &lt;br /&gt;&bull; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/avtomobilnye-aksessuary/audio-1/magnitola&quot;&gt;magnitola&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; avtomobilning old paneliga musiqa tinglash imkonini beruvchi qurilmalar. Bugungi kunda ular deyarli har qanday avtomobilning ajralmas qismidir. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Agar siz avtomobil akustikasini sotib olishni rejalashtirgan bo&rsquo;lsangiz bizning veb-saytimiz orqali kerakli qurilmalarni tanlashingiz mumkin. Mashinada ishlatiladigan akustika osongina o&#039;rnatilib siz uchun uzoq vaqt xizmat qiladi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Qo&#039;shimcha funktsiyalar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Musiqani ijro etish avtomobil akustikasining yagona vazifasi emas. Ushbu toifaga kiruvchi qurilmalar quyidagilar bilan jihozlanishi mumkin: &lt;br /&gt; &bull; Lokatsiya aniqlash. GPS- yordamida; &lt;br /&gt; &bull; Ekran bilan jihozlash - bu sizga videoni tomosha qilishga imkonini beradi. &lt;br /&gt;Avtoulovdagi akustik va elektron uskunalar foydalanish jarayonida bir qator afzalliklarga ega: &lt;br /&gt;&bull; o&#039;rnatish va ishlatish qulayligi; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; xavfsizligi; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; narxning arzonligi; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;Olcha.uz onlayn-do&#039;koni avto jihozlar saxifasida avtomobil uchun audio qurilmalarining keng assortimentini taklif etadi. Avatar, Sony, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/manufacturer/pioneer&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pioneer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Edifier, Deaf Bonce, Urat, Hertz, Kenwood, Dl Audio,Dynamic State boshqa brendlar mahsulotlarini mutaxassislarimiz bilan maslahatlashgan holda xarid qilishingiz mumkin. Biz O&rsquo;zbekiston bo&#039;ylab yetkazib berishni amalga oshiramiz, tovarni muddatli to&rsquo;lov asosida xarid qilishingiz mumkin. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qayerdan xarid qilsam bo&rsquo;ladi?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Bu yerda siz kunning istalgan vaqtida tovarlarni tanlashingiz va buyurtma qilishingiz va qulay tarzda yetkazib berishni tashkil qilishingiz mumkin. Bizning onlayn magazinimiz buyurtmalarni mijozlarga eng tezkor tarzda Toshkent, Andijon, Samarqand, Buxoro, Farg&rsquo;ona, Namangan, Surxondaryo, Qashqadaryo, Navoiy, Sirdaryo, Jizzax va Nukus ya&rsquo;ni Qoraqalpog&rsquo;iston Respublikasi bo&rsquo;ylab tezkor yetkazib beriladi. Buyurtmangiz Toshkent shaxrida yashovchilar uchun 12 soat ichida, viloyatlar uchun esa 2-3 kun davomida olib boriladi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&#039;lumotlar onlayn chatda yoki +998(71)2022021 raqami orqali o&#039;zingizni qiziqtirgan savollarga javob olishingiz mumkin. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
