        ('Sport uskunalar', 'oborudovanie-dlya-sporta', 81, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport uskunalari&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport uskunalari - bu jismoniy mashqlar samaradorligi va sifatini oshirish uchun mo&#039;ljallangan sport jihozlari. Sport mahsulotlari keng assortimentdagi mahsulot va jihozlarni o&#039;z ichiga oladi. Ko&#039;pgina mahsulotlar (masalan, fitnes,gimnastika,yoga) turli xil sport turlari uchun ishlatilishi mumkin, ba&#039;zilari (yugurish yo&rsquo;lakchalari,velotrenajyorlar, skameykalar) alohida e&#039;tiborga ega. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sport uskunalarining turlari:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; yoga uchun. Bunday mashg&#039;ulotlar uchun sizga gimnastik gilam kerak, shuningdek, fitbol, fitnes to&rsquo;plari, roller, yoga kamari yoki elastik tasma kerak bo&#039;lishi mumkin; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; kuch mashqlari uchun. Kuch-quvvat mashqlari paytida mushaklarni rivojlantirish uchun rezina gantellar va ko&rsquo;p funksiyali kuchni mashq qilish uskunasi sotib olishga arziydi; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; gimnastika uchun. Gimnastika tananing chidamliligini rivojlantiradi va mushaklaringizni yaxshi holatda saqlashga imkon beradi. Ushbu maqsadlar uchun fitnes disklari, gimnastika tayoqlari, CrossFit arqonlari va boshqa qurilmalar ishlatiladi. &lt;br /&gt;&bull; qo&rsquo;shimcha tarzda bo&rsquo;yin mushaklari uchun trenajyor,elliptik trenajyor,velotrenajyor,skameykalar xarid qilishingiz mumkin. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sport mahsulotlarini tanlash mezonlari:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Avvalo, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/sporttovary&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;sport&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;mashg&#039;ulotlaringiz turiga qarab jihozni tanlang. Shuni unutmangki, mashg&#039;ulotdan oldin tana qizib olishi kerak, buning uchun siz aksessuarlarni yoki yugurish yo&rsquo;lakchalari, velotrenajyor, elliptik trenajyor singari jihozlarni ham olishingiz mumkin. &lt;br /&gt;Og&#039;irligingiz va bo&#039;yingizga qarab sport jihozlarini tanlang. Ba&#039;zi mahsulotlar uchun (qadam platformalari, sakrash arqonlari) balandlik, uzunlik va boshqa o&#039;lchamlarni sozlash mumkin. &lt;br /&gt;Sport jihozlaridan foydalanish uchun qulay bo&#039;lishi va sizga xavf yaratmasligi kerak. &lt;br /&gt;O&rsquo;zbekistonda sport uskunalarni Olcha.uz onlayn-do&#039;konida tanlashingiz va sotib olishingiz mumkin - biz taniqli jahon ishlab chiqaruvchilari Fitland,Volksgym,Marshal Lord Fitness, PowerGym,Velolarning sport mashqlari uchun qo&rsquo;llaniladigan asbob uskunlarning keng assortimentini taklif qilamiz. Shuningdek, bizda sport aksessuarlari, basketbol, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/sporttovary/vse-dlya-futbola&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;futbol&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, voleybol,tennis, suzish anjomlari mavjud.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qanday xarid qilsam bo&rsquo;ladi?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Onlayn do&#039;konimizda uydan chiqmagan holda veb saytimiz orqali buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Agar sizning byudjetingizda bir vaqtning o&#039;zida bunday mablag&rsquo; yo&rsquo;q bo&#039;lsa, siz ortiqcha to&#039;lovlarsiz bo&#039;lib-bo&#039;lib to&#039;lash imkoniyatiga egasiz. O&rsquo;zbekiston bo&rsquo;ylab yetkazib berish xizmati mavjud. Manzilga qarab 4 soatdan 2 ish kunigacha yetkazib beriladi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumot quyidagi raqam bilan: +998 71-2022021 yoki saytimiz orqali chatdan ma&#039;lumot olishingiz mumkin &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
        ('Skeytlar va Samokatlar', 'skeyty-i-samokaty', 185, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Samokat va skeytlar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Ko&#039;pgina bolalar velosipeddan ko&#039;ra samokat va skeytlarni afzal ko&#039;radilar. Sababi, uni tezda o&#039;rganib olish &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/sporttovary/giroskuter/skeyty-i-skutery&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;velosipeddan&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;ko&rsquo;ra ancha oson. Ko&rsquo;rinishi ham chiroyli dizaynda bo&rsquo;lib, yengil va ixchamligi bilan ajralib turadi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Asosiy modellarning umumiy ko&#039;rinishi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jismoniy qobiliyat va yoshga qarab, samokatlarni ikki yoki uchta g&#039;ildirak bilan sotib olish mumkin. Barcha modellar deyarli bir xil ko&rsquo;rinishdagi dizaynga ega: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; rul; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; oyoqlar uchun platformalar; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; g&#039;ildiraklar. &lt;br /&gt;Uch g&#039;ildirakli samokatlarda kattalar yordami uchun tutqich bo&#039;lishi mumkin, bu model ikki yoshga to&#039;lgan va endigina minishni o&#039;rgana boshlagan va muvozanatni yaxshi saqlamaydigan bolalar uchun juda mos keladi. Katta bolalar uchun ikki g&#039;ildirakli samokatlarga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin, ular farzandingizni erkin sayr qilish imkoniyati bilan birga, tezligini rivojlantirishga ham yordam beradi. Bu to&#039;rt yoshdan oshgan bolalar uchun eng yaxshi tanlovdir, ularni minish uchun siz muvozanatni yaxshi ushlab turishingiz kerak.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Asosiy xususiyatlar &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; G&#039;ildiraklar rezina prokladkalar bilan plastikdan tayyorlanishi yoki faqat kauchukdan yasalgan bo&rsquo;lishi mumkin, tanlovni foydalanish joyiga qarab belgilanish kerak. Asfaltda haydash uchun kauchukli plastik g&#039;ildiraklar mos keladi, agar harakat tuproq yo&#039;lda bo&#039;lsa, rezinalarni tanlash yaxshi natija beradi. G&#039;ildiraklarning diametri va qalinligi muozanatga ta&#039;sir qiladi. Ular qanchalik kichik va ingichka bo&#039;lsa, uni boshqarish osonroq bo&#039;ladi. Lekin kichkina kenglikdagi g&#039;ildiraklarda muvozanatni saqlash qiyinroq. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Bolaning balandligiga qarab, siz rulning balandligini tanlashingiz kerak. Bugungi kunda ba&rsquo;zi modellarni o&rsquo;z xoxishingizga ko&rsquo;ra rullini baland-pastlatishingiz mumkin. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Oyoqlar uchun platforma ishlab chiqarishda plastmassa, metall yoki ularning kombinatsiyasidan foydalanish mumkin. Shuni aytib o&rsquo;tish kerakki, misol tariqasida, plastik platformalar eng kichik bolalar uchun mo&#039;ljallangan modellarda mavjud. Katta yoshdagilar uchun taglik metalldan yasalgan, bunday samokatlar yanada bardoshli va ular rulda yoki orqa g&#039;ildirakda joylashgan tormoz tizimi bilan ta&rsquo;minlangan bo&rsquo;lib yuqori tezlikdagi noxush vaziyatlarni oldini oladi. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Samokatlar qatlanadigan dizaynga ega bo&#039;lishi ham mumkin, buning natijasida saqlash vaqtida u juda kam joy egallaydi, uni mashinada osongina olib yursa bo&rsquo;ladi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;onlayn-do&#039;konida samokat va skeytlarga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Saytda har xil yosh uchun bolalar transportining turli modellari arzon narxlarda taqdim etilgan. Bu yerda siz Samarqand, Andijon yoki O&rsquo;zbekistonning istalgan shahridan ishonch va kafolat bilan xaridni amalga oshirasiz. Buyurtmangiz Toshkent shaxrida yashovchilar uchun 12 soat ichida, viloyatlar uchun esa 2-3 kun davomida olib boriladi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&#039;lumotlar onlayn chatda yoki +998(71)2022021 raqami orqali o&#039;zingizni qiziqtirgan savollarga javob olishingiz mumkin. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
