        ('Onalar va go‘daklar uchun tovarlar', 'detskie-aksessuary', 185, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;O&#039;zbekistonda onalar va go&rsquo;daklar uchun eng yaxshi tovarlar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Shirin chaqalog&#039;ingizni tug&#039;ruqxonadan uyga olib kelishga tayyorgarlik ko&#039;rayotganingizda Yangi tug&#039;ilgan chaqaloqqa munosib g&#039;amxo&#039;rlik qilish uchun nima qilish kerakligi va uni nimadan boshlash mumkinligini bilmayotgan bo&rsquo;lsangiz, Olcha.uz sizga ko&rsquo;maklashadi. Ota-onalar chaqaloqni bu dunyoda kelishidan to voyaga yetkazguncha barcha zarur narsalar bilan ta&#039;minlab g&rsquo;amxurlik qilishni o&rsquo;z zimmalariga oladilar. Bolalar mahsulotlari bozorda keng ko&#039;lamda taqdim etiladi. Ba&#039;zida ota-onalar yangi tug&#039;ilgan chaqaloq uchun &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/moda-i-aksessuary&quot;&gt;kiyim-kechak&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/mebel-1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mebel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, aksessuarlar, gigiena, xavfsizlik va parvarish vositalarini tanlashda turli muommolarga duch keladilar. Onalar va go&rsquo;daklar uchun eng sifatli va arzon narxlarda tovarlarni Olcha.uz internet-do&#039;konida topishingiz mumkin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Bolaga nima sotib olish kerak&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Bir yosh orasidagi chaqaloqlar uchun narsalarni alohida e&#039;tibor bilan tanlash kerak, chunki ular hali tashqi muhitga moslashmagan va allergiya, terining tirnalishiga va dermatitga eng moyil payti hisoblanadi. Sotib olayotgan kiyimlar tabiiy, havo o&rsquo;tkazadigan materiallardan iborat bo&#039;lishi kerak. Bizning veb-saytimizda taqdim etilgan mahsulotlar yillar davomida sinovdan o&rsquo;tgan Tomme Tippee, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/manufacturer/panasonic&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Panasonic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Comotomo, Lionelo, Al Huda kabi brendlarning mahsulotlaridir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ota-onalar uchun biz bolalar mahsulotlarining keng assortimentini taklif qilamiz: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; oziqlantirish uchun (shishalar, emziklilarga stakan); &lt;br /&gt;&bull; gigiyena va parvarishlash vositalari (turli markadagi tagliklar, bolalar uchun gigiyenik prokladkalar, aspiratorlar, elektron termometrlar); &lt;br /&gt;&bull; mebel (beshiklar va choyshablar); &lt;br /&gt;&bull; sut sog&rsquo;uvchi uskunalar; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; cho&#039;milish buyumlari; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; aylanish va sayohat uchun (aravachalar va avtomobil o&#039;rindiqlari.) &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qanday mahsulotlar yangi tug&#039;ilgan chaqaloqni munosib parvarish qilishga yordam beradi &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Yangi tug&#039;ilgan chaqaloq alohida e&rsquo;tiborga muhtoj. Bola tug&rsquo;ilishi bilanoq atrofida darhol ko&#039;plab uy-ro&#039;zg&#039;or buyumlari paydo bo&#039;ladi. Siz ularni bir joydan, arzon narxlarda sotib olishingiz mumkin. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quyidagi narsalarning mavjudligi chaqaloq tug&#039;ilgandan keyin sizga kerak bo&rsquo;ladi: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; Oziqlantiruvchi idishlar. Ko&#039;krak sutini yig&#039;ish, saqlash, shuningdek, yangi tug&#039;ilgan chaqaloqlarni oziqlantirish uchun maxsus mo&#039;ljallangan. Ular sut sog&#039;ishni rejalashtirgan har bir kishi uchun zarurdir. Ushbu mahsulotlarda sut uzoq vaqt ishonchli saqlashnishi mumkin. &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Gigiyena va parvarish vositalari (bolalarni parvarish qilish vositalari, soch uchun taroq, cho&rsquo;tka, tirnoq qaychisi);&lt;br /&gt;&bull; Go&rsquo;daklar yotishi uchun; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Sut sog&rsquo;uvchi uskunalar tug&#039;ruqdan keyingi laktatsiya davrida onalar uchun zarurdir. Laktatsiya - bu bolaning ovqatlanishini ta&#039;minlaydigan ayolda sut hosil bo&#039;ladigan fiziologik jarayon. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bolalar uchun zarur bo&#039;lgan barcha narsalarni bizdan eng yaxshi narxlarda buyurtma qilishingiz mumkin. Bizda muddatli to&rsquo;lov asosida ortiqcha hujjatlarsiz ham xarid amalga oshiriladi. Bundan tashqari, bizda taqdim etilgan barcha mahsulotlar sifatli brend mahsulotlari hisoblanadi. &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; onlayn-do&#039;kon sifatida ishlaydi, shuning uchun bu yerda tovarlarga onlayn buyurtma berish mumkin.Toshkent va O&rsquo;zbekistonning boshqa shaharlariga ham bir necha ish kuni ichida buyurtma belgilangan manzilga yetkaziladi. Bizning do&#039;konimizda bolalar buyumlaridan tashqari, istalgan &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/bytovaya-tekhnika-dlya-doma&quot;&gt;maishiy texnika&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; va boshqa jihozlarni topishingiz mumkin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&#039;lumotlar onlayn chatda yoki +998(71)2022021 raqami orqali o&#039;zingizni qiziqtirgan savollarga javob olishingiz mumkin. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
