        ('Sport ozuqalari', 'sportivnoe-pitanie', 81, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport ozuqalari&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport ozuqalari - bu sportchilar va faol hayot tarzi bilan shug&#039;ullanadiganlar uchun mo&#039;ljallangan ozuqaviy qo&#039;shimchalar. Jismoniy ish faoliyatini yaxshilash, mushaklar hajmini oshirish, metabolizmni normallashtirish maqsadida qo&rsquo;llaniladi. &lt;br /&gt;Bizning onlayn magazinimiz buyurtmalarni mijozlarga eng tezkor tarzda Toshkent, Andijon, Samarqand, Buxoro, Farg&rsquo;ona, Namangan, Surxondaryo, Qashqadaryo, Navoiy, Sirdaryo, Jizzax va Nukus ya&rsquo;ni Qoraqalpog&rsquo;iston Respublikasi bo&rsquo;ylab tezkor yetkazib beriladi. Buyurtmangiz Toshkent shaxrida yashovchilar uchun 12 soat ichida, viloyatlar uchun esa 2-3 kun davomida olib boriladi. &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Katalogda&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;- vazn ortishi, vazn yo&#039;qotish, tiklanish uchun sport ozuqalarini tanlashingiz mumkin. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; aminokislotalar - L-karnitin, BCAA, arginin, kreatin, protein, L-glutamin, beta-alanin, aminokislotalar komplekslari; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; geynerlar, uglevod aralashmalari; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; izotonik, energetik ichimliklar konsentratlari; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; vitamin-mineral, mashg&#039;ulotdan keyingi, mashg&#039;ulotdan oldingi komplekslar; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; bo&#039;g&#039;inlar uchun vositalar - kollagen, glyukozamin, moddalar aralashmalari; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; oqsil - aminokislotalar bilan oqsil konsentratlari;kreatin; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; Omega 3; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; energiya - taurin, glitsin, monosaxaridlar bilan. &lt;br /&gt;&bull; sheykerlar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Bizning maqsadimiz eng arzon narxda sifatli sport ozuqalarini taklif qilishdir. Biz faqat ishonchli ishlab chiqaruvchi brendlar bilan ishlaymiz. Biz iste&#039;molchining ehtiyojlarini qondirish va yaxshi natijaga erishish uchun kerakli bo&rsquo;lgan mahsulotlarni taklif etamiz.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;To&#039;g&#039;ri mahsulotlarni qanday tanlash mumkin?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Muayyan mahsulotni tanlashda qiynalayotgan bo&#039;lsangiz +998712022021 raqamiga qo&#039;ng&#039;iroq qiling va siz do&#039;konimizning tajribali xodimlaridan o&rsquo;zingiz qiziqtirgan maslahat olishingiz mumkin. Shaxsiy xususiyatlaringiz va maqsadlaringizni hisobga olgan holda siz uchun eng mos bo&#039;lgan sport ozuqalarini tanlashda har doim maslahat olishingiz mumkin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;O&rsquo;zbekistonning ishonchli hamda sifatli buyumlar yetkazib beradigan Olcha.uz online do&#039;konimizda qulay narxlarda sotib oling. &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 2017-yildan beri bozorda faoliyat yuritayotgan kompaniya bo&lsquo;lsa-da, bu boradagi xodimlarning tajribasi 16 yilga yetadi. Biz har xil brendlar va yaxshi narx segmentlari bilan ishlaymiz va har bir mijozga o&#039;z byudjetiga, hisobiga mos variantni taklif qilishimiz mumkin. Endi sizda to&rsquo;liq summa bo&rsquo;lmagan taqdirda to&rsquo;lov muddatini uzaytirgan holda to&rsquo;lash imkoniyatiga egasiz. Buning uchun passport hamda bank kartasi kifoya.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
