        ('Boshqa asboblar', 'prochee-1', 479, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Boshqa asboblar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Har qanday binoning qurish va ta&rsquo;mirlashda u hoh sanoat,hoh uyda bo&rsquo;lsin uning uchun zarur asbob va uskunalar to&rsquo;plamiga ehtiyoj kata bo&rsquo;lib bormoqda. Qurilish va ta&rsquo;mirlashda ishlatiladigan asbob uskunalarning turlari juda ko&rsquo;p va har birining o&rsquo;z o&rsquo;rni, vazifasi bor. Har qanday qurilish ishlarida katta uskunalar pnevmatik purkagich, elektr havo puflagich,quvur kesgich kabilar bilan deyarli ko&rsquo;zga ko&rsquo;rinmaydigan pilka, sverlo singari uskunlarning keng assortimentini olcha.uz online do&rsquo;konida xarid qilish imkoniyatiga egasiz. olcha.uz &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;katalogida&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;siz eng yaxshi brendlar asosida istalgan turdagi asbob uskunalarga uydan chiqmagan holda buyurtma berish orqali yetkazib berish xizmatidan foydalanishingiz mumkin. Ushbu sahifada mavjud buyumlar orasida siz qurilish-o&rsquo;lchash mahsulotlari (o&rsquo;lchov lentasi), turli vazifani bajaruvchi pistoletlar,yog&rsquo;och kesish uchun arralarning istalgan o&rsquo;lchami, shpatel, bolg&#039;a, shtroborez, otvertka, elektrolobzik singari mingdan ortiq jihozlarni topishingiz mumkin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; online do&rsquo;koni hozirda bozorda o&rsquo;z o&rsquo;rniga ega, ishonchli hamda arzon narxdagi tovarlarni yetkazib beruvchi online do&rsquo;konlar orasida oldinlab bormoqda. 2017-yildan beri bozorda faoliyat yuritayotgan kompaniya bo&lsquo;lsa-da, bu boradagi xodimlarning tajribasi 16 yilga teng.Qurilish va ta&rsquo;mirlash uchun