        ('Elektr arralar', 'elektropily-1', 479, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Elektr arralar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Elektr arra yog&#039;och, plastmassa va boshqa q&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;urilish materiallarini arralash uchun mo&#039;ljallangan ko&#039;p qirrali asbobdir. Elektr arralar keng ko&rsquo;lamli bo&rsquo;lib, sanoat-qurilish sohasida, yog&#039;ochni qayta ishlash korxonalarida, uy va bog&rsquo; uchun foydali uskuna sifatida ishlatiladi. &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;online do&rsquo;koni elektr arralarning keng turini arzon narxlarda taqdim etadi. Barchasi ta&rsquo;mirlash va qurilish uchun nomli sahifada siz istalgan turdagi asbob-uskunaga uyingizdan chiqmagan holda buyurtma berishingiz mumkin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ko&rsquo;pgina qurilish vosita singari, ular ham uy xo&rsquo;jaligi uchun maishiy (bog&rsquo; uchun) va professional elektr arralarga bo&#039;linadi: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bog&rsquo; arralari zanjirli arralarning eng yengil turi. Ular novdalarni kesishda, kichik diametrli o&#039;tinni arralashda ishni tez va samarali yakunlaydigan eng xavfsiz va vaqti-vaqti bilan foydalanish uchun mo&#039;ljallangan uskuna sifatida qo&rsquo;llaniladi. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professional&lt;/strong&gt; - kundalik foydalanish uchun mo&#039;ljallangan juda ishonchli vosita. Ular kuchli dvigatel sababli yuqori ishlash tezligiga ega. U qurilish va duradgorlik ishlarida, shuningdek, tishli arralardan foydalanish mumkin bo&#039;lmagan holatlarda, shuningdek, bino ichida ham faol qo&#039;llaniladi. &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Elektr arrasini qanday tanlash mumkin?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Elektr arra sotib olayotganda uning quvvat kuchiga e&rsquo;tibor qarating. Bu ko&rsquo;rsatkich uning ishlash tezligiga ta&rsquo;sir ko&rsquo;rsatadi. Arra tishlari qalinligini ham e&rsquo;tibor bering. Shina uzunligi odatda 30-40 sm uzunlikdagisi eng maqbul variant hisoblanadi. Boshqa turda esa asbob harakat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;chanligi kamaytiradi. Quvvatlantirish manbaiga ham turlicha bo&rsquo;lib, tarmoqqa ulanadigan, akkumliyatorli, batareykali bo&rsquo;lishi mumkin. Shuningdek siz elekt arra og&rsquo;irligi va o&rsquo;lchamini ham o&rsquo;z xoxishingizga ko&rsquo;ra tanlashingiz mumkin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;O&rsquo;zbekistonda elekt arralarni Olcha.uz onlayn-do&#039;konida tanlashingiz va sotib olishingiz mumkin - biz taniqli jahon ishlab chiqaruvchilari Milwaukee, &lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/manufacturer/bosch&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bosch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Total, Crown, EPA, RTRMAX, INGCO brendlarining qurlish va ta&rsquo;mirlashda qo&rsquo;llaniladigan asbob va uskunlarning keng assortimentini taklif qilamiz. Do&#039;kon katalogida akkumlyatorli arra, batareyali arra, diskli arra, dumaloq arra, simsiz arra, o&rsquo;rnatiladigan arra kabi mahsulotlarning batafsil tavsifi, fotosurati va narxi mavjud.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qanday xarid qilsam bo&rsquo;ladi?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Onlayn do&#039;konimizda uydan chiqmagan holda veb saytimiz orqali buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Qo&rsquo;shimcha tarzda boshqa barcha ta&rsquo;mirlash va qurulish uchun asbob va jihozlarni xarid qilishingiz mumkin. Agar sizning byudjetingizda bir vaqtning o&#039;zida bunday mablag&rsquo; yo&rsquo;q bo&#039;lsa, siz ortiqcha to&#039;lovlarsiz bo&#039;lib-bo&#039;lib to&#039;lash imkoniyatiga egasiz. Bu yerda siz Samarqand, Andijon, Buxoro yoki O&rsquo;zbekistonning istalgan shahridan ishonch va kafolat bilan xaridni amalga oshirasiz. Buyurtmangiz Toshkent shahrida yashovchilar uchun 12 soat ichida, viloyatlar uchun esa 2-3 kun davomida olib boriladi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumot quyidagi raqam bilan: +998 71-2022021 yoki saytimiz orqali chatdan ma&#039;lumot olishingiz mumkin &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
