        ('Kuchni mashq qilish uskunalar', 'silovye-trenazhery', 381, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport uskunalari&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Sport uskunalari - bu jismoniy mashqlar samaradorligi va sifatini oshirish uchun mo&#039;ljallangan sport jihozlari. Sport mahsulotlari keng assortimentdagi mahsulot va jihozlarni o&#039;z ichiga oladi. Ko&#039;pgina mahsulotlar (masalan, fitnes,gimnastika,yoga) turli xil sport turlari uchun ishlatilishi mumkin, ba&#039;zilari (yugurish yo&rsquo;lakchalari,velotrenajyorlar, skameykalar) alohida e&#039;tiborga ega.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sport uskunalarining turlari:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; yoga uchun. Bunday mashg&#039;ulotlar uchun sizga gimnastik gilam kerak, shuningdek, fitbol, fitnes to&rsquo;plari, roller, yoga kamari yoki elastik tasma kerak bo&#039;lishi mumkin;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; kuch mashqlari uchun. Kuch-quvvat mashqlari paytida mushaklarni rivojlantirish uchun rezina gantellar va ko&rsquo;p funksiyali kuchni mashq qilish uskunasi sotib olishga arziydi;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; gimnastika uchun. Gimnastika tananing chidamliligini rivojlantiradi va mushaklaringizni yaxshi holatda saqlashga imkon beradi. Ushbu maqsadlar uchun fitnes disklari, gimnastika tayoqlari, CrossFit arqonlari va boshqa qurilmalar ishlatiladi.&lt;br /&gt;&bull; qo&rsquo;shimcha tarzda bo&rsquo;yin mushaklari uchun trenajyor,elliptik trenajyor,velotrenajyor,skameykalar xarid qilishingiz mumkin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sport mahsulotlarini tanlash mezonlari:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&qu