        ('Qog‘oz mahsulotlari', 'bumazhnaya-produktsiya', 196, '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qog&rsquo;oz mahsulotlari&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/knigi/istoricheskie-knigi&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tarix&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/a&gt;darslaridan bilganimizdek, qog&#039;ozning narxi har doim ancha yuqori bo&#039;lgan, chunki uni ishlab chiqarish uchun maxsus jihozlar, yuqori sifatli xom ashyo va ma&#039;lum ko&#039;nikmalar kerak bo&rsquo;lgan. Qog&rsquo;ozni ishlab chiqarish bilan shug&#039;ullangan hunarmandlar, ularning darhol badavlat odamlarga yetkazib berishgan. Endi hamma narsa ancha sodda, chunki qog&#039;oz mahsulotlarini ishlab chiqarish bilan shug&#039;ullanadigan ko&#039;plab kompaniyalar mavjud, ammo sifat hamma joyda bir xil emas. Ofis qog&#039;ozini arzonga sotib olishingiz, lekin ayni paytda uning barcha xususiyatlaridan to&#039;liq qoniqishingiz uchun do&#039;konimiz faqat eng yaxshi ishlab chiqaruvchilarning tovarlarini taqdim etadi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Barcha muhim parametrlar: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&bull; yorqinlik; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; format; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; hajmi; &lt;br /&gt;&bull; oqlik.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qog&#039;oz mahsulotlarining assortimenti&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Hamma odamlar, kasbi, ijtimoiy mavqei va yoshidan qat&#039;i nazar, qog&rsquo;oz mahsulotlaridan foydalanadilar.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hammaga:&lt;/strong&gt; maktabgacha yoshdagi bolalar, maktab va uydagi o&#039;quvchilar va o&#039;qituvchilar, talabalar, ofis xodimlari va boshqa ko&#039;plab toifadagi odamlar ulardan foydalanadilar. Bizda maktab o&#039;quvchilari uchun umumiy, musiqiy va mavzuli daftarlar, shuningdek, rasm chizish uchun albomlar va kundaliklar mavjud. Turli ko&rsquo;rinishdagi &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/kantselyarskie-tovary/bumazhnaya-produktsiya/bloknoty&quot;&gt;bloknot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, anketa, jurnal, konvertlarni endi siz gadjetingiz orqali osongina tanlashingiz mumkin. Qog&rsquo;oz mahsulotlarining keng assortimentiga ega bo&#039;lgan onlayn-do&#039;konimizda xaridlarni amalga oshirish sizga ancha maqbul keladi. Ularning yuqori sifati, arzon narxlari va bir vaqtning o&lsquo;zida hamma narsani bir joydan sotib olish imkoniyati xaridorlarni qulayligi va arzonligi bilan o&lsquo;ziga tortadi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Bolalar chiroyli daftarlarga ega bo&#039;lishni xohlashadi. Biz ularning istaklarini inobatga olamiz. Farzandingiz uchun yorqin rangdagi ajoyib va betakror chizmalar bilan daftarlarni tanlashingiz mumkin. Daftarlarning keng assortimenti birinchi sinf o&#039;quvchilarini ham, o&#039;n birinchi sinf o&#039;quvchilarini ham e&#039;tiborsiz qoldirmaydi&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olcha.uz&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;internet&nbsp;do&rsquo;konida uydan chiqmagan holda saytdan buyurtma berish orqali siz tezda tovarni qo&rsquo;lingizga olasiz. Farzandlaringizga bo&#039;sh vaqtingizni bag&#039;ishlang, ular doimo ota-onalarining birga vaqt o&rsquo;tkazishni intiqlik bilan kutishadi. Bizda oila byudjetini tejaydigan arzon daftarlar bor va siz biz bilan yanada chiroyli xaridlarni amalga oshirishingiz mumkin.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&rsquo;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumotlar saytdan yoki +998(71)2022021 raqamlari orqali olishingiz mumkin. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
