ue=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bizda futbol va boshqa sport anjomlarining keng turi mavjud. Ularni tanlashda albatta mahsulotning xususiyatlariga e&rsquo;tibor qaratishingiz lozim. Masalan,&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category/moda-i-aksessuary/obuv&quot;&gt;poyabzal&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;kabi muhim futbol anjominini tanlashga ehtiyotkorlik bilan yondashishingiz kerak. Yuqori sifatli butsalar futbolchining harakat tezligiga, barqarorligi va salomatligi xavfsizligiga ijobiy ta&#039;sir ko&#039;rsatadi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Qanday xarid qilsam bo&rsquo;ladi?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;Onlayn do&#039;konimizda uydan chiqmagan holda veb saytimiz orqali buyurtma berishingiz mumkin.&lt;a href=&quot;https://olcha.uz/oz/category&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Katalogda&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;turli xil modellar bo&rsquo;lib ularning narxi, ko&rsquo;rinishi va ranglari mavjud. Qo&rsquo;shimcha tarzda boshqa sport anjomlarini ham taqdim etamiz.Agar sizning byudjetingizda bir vaqtning o&#039;zida bunday mablag&rsquo; yo&rsquo;q bo&#039;lsa, siz ortiqcha to&#039;lovlarsiz bo&#039;lib-bo&#039;lib to&#039;lash imkoniyatiga egasiz. O&rsquo;zbekiston bo&rsquo;ylab yetkazib berish xizmati mavjud. Manzilga qarab 4 soatdan 2 ish kunigacha yetkazib beriladi.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-value=&quot;{&quot; data-sheets-userformat=&quot;{&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qo&#039;shimcha ma&rsquo;lumot quyidagi raqam bilan: +998 71-2022021 yoki saytimiz orqali chatdan ma&#039;lumot olishingiz mumkin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
