        ('Yumshoq mebel', 'myagkaya-mebel', 643, '&lt;div class=&quot;flex items-baseline mt-2.5 md:mb-5 lg:mb-10&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;md:text-3.5xl lg:text-42px mr-7 font-bold text-black&quot;&gt;Yumshoq mebel&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;grid grid-cols-5 gap-4 pb-10&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;relative col-span-1&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;open-sideBar overflow-y-auto h-full bg-white w-full pr-2&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;w-full&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;lg:col-span-1&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;bg-white p-5 lg:p-0 overflow-y-auto transform duration-300 translate-x-0&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-4 &quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;flex justify-between mb-4 cursor-pointer&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yumshoq mebel&lt;/strong&gt;-yumshoq elementga ega o&#039;tirish va yotish uchun qulay mebel mahsulotlarining umumiy nomi. Yumshoq mebellarga quyidagilar kiradi: divanlar-ko&#039;rpa-to&#039;shaklar, divanlar, kreslolar-to&#039;shaklar, dam olish stullari, divanlar, ottomanlar, skameykalar, ziyofatlar.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;flex justify-between mb-4 cursor-pointer&quot; data-v-9c579f06=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Bizdan xarid qanday amalga oshiriladi?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ko&lsquo;rib turganingizdek, xaridingizni qilish uchun sotiladigan tovarlar va modellarning yetarli turlari mavjud. Ammo ko&lsquo;pchilik hali ham onlayn xaridlar formatiga ishonmaydi. Kimdir texnikaning tavsiflangan xususiyatlariga ishonch hosil qilmaydi, boshqalari kredit olishning iloji yo&lsquo;q deb o&lsquo;ylashadi, agar to&lsquo;liq summa miqdori mavjud bo&lsquo;lmasa, kimdir odatda tovarlar unga yetib borishiga shubha qiladi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&laquo;Olcha.uz&raquo; onlayn-do&lsquo;koni rasmiy ravishda ishlaydi, biz tovarlarga kafolat beramiz va sotishdan keyingi servis xizmatni taqdim etamiz. Muddatli bo&lsquo;lib to&lsquo;lashga kelsak, onlayn-biznes uchun bu qoidadan ko&lsquo;ra ko&lsquo;proq istisno, ammo biz uzoq vaqtdan beri, hatto banklarni jalb qilmasdan, kechiktirilgan to&lsquo;lovlarni hisoblamasdan ham muddatli bo&lsquo;lib to&lsquo;lash xaridlarni amalga oshirmoqdamiz. Ya&rsquo;ni, siz oflayn do&lsquo;konda muntazam xarid qilish bilan, bir xil shartlarga ega bo&lsquo;lasiz, bundan tashqari, bir nechta - maishiy texnika uchun arzon narxlar va bir necha tugmani bosish orqali uyingizdan chiqmasdan buyurtma berish imkoniyati. Narxlarga kelsak, shubhalanish uchun hech qanday sabab yo&lsquo;q. Onlayn platformada ishlaganimiz sababli, biz operasion xarajatlarni sezilarli darajada kamaytirishga qodirmiz, bozorda mavjud bo&lsquo;lgan bir xil tovarlarni arzonroq narxda sotish mumkin. Texnologiyalar oldinga siljiydi, onlayn biznes tez o&lsquo;sib bormoqda va onlayn xarid qilish nafaqat foydali va qulay, balki xavfsizdir.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Muddatli bo&lsquo;lib to&lsquo;lash qanday rasmiylashtiriladi?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Xaridni bo&lsquo;lib to&lsquo;lash uchun siz faqat pasportni taqdim etishingiz va bank oylik kartangizga ega bo&lsquo;lishingiz kerak. To&lsquo;lovlar uchun tegishli muddatni (3 oydan 12 oygacha) va birinchi to&lsquo;lov miqdorini o&lsquo;zingiz tanlashingiz mumkin. Hammasi onlayn tarzda amalga oshiriladi - tafsilotlar tegishli bo&lsquo;limda tasvirlangan va bizning xodimlarimiz jarayonda sizga hamroh bo&lsquo;lishadi. Uskunalar uchun arzon, ammo ishonchli yangi buyumlarni tanlang, biz O&lsquo;zbekistonning istalgan nuqtasiga tez yetkazib beramiz.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '2022-12-11 18:07:09', '2022-12-11 18:07:09'),
